### Create a new reservation
POST http://localhost:8080/api/reservations
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "customerId": 1,
  "vehicleId": 1,
  "startDate": "2024-10-01",
  "endDate": "2024-10-05",
  "pickupLocation": "Main Office - 123 Downtown Ave",
  "returnLocation": "Main Office - 123 Downtown Ave",
  "pickupTime": "2024-10-01T09:00:00",
  "returnTime": "2024-10-05T17:00:00",
  "specialRequests": "Please have the car cleaned before pickup",
  "insuranceIncluded": true,
  "additionalDriver": false,
  "gpsIncluded": true,
  "childSeatIncluded": false
}

### Create reservation with all extras
