### Get all reservations
GET http://localhost:8080/api/reservations

### Get reservation by ID
GET http://localhost:8080/api/reservations/1

### Get reservation by reservation number
GET http://localhost:8080/api/reservations/number/RES1725743325389

### Get customer's reservations
GET http://localhost:8080/api/reservations/customer/1

### Get vehicle's reservations
GET http://localhost:8080/api/reservations/vehicle/1

### Get reservations by status
GET http://localhost:8080/api/reservations/status/PENDING

### Get confirmed reservations
GET http://localhost:8080/api/reservations/status/CONFIRMED

### Get completed reservations
GET http://localhost:8080/api/reservations/status/COMPLETED

### Get current active reservations
GET http://localhost:8080/api/reservations/active

### Get upcoming reservations
GET http://localhost:8080/api/reservations/upcoming

### Get overdue reservations
GET http://localhost:8080/api/reservations/overdue

### Get today's pickups
GET http://localhost:8080/api/reservations/today/pickups

### Get today's returns
GET http://localhost:8080/api/reservations/today/returns

### Check vehicle availability
GET http://localhost:8080/api/reservations/availability?vehicleId=1&startDate=2024-10-15&endDate=2024-10-20

### Check vehicle availability (conflicting dates)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/reservations/availability?vehicleId=1&startDate=2024-10-02&endDate=2024-10-04

### Confirm reservation
PATCH http://localhost:8080/api/reservations/1/confirm?employeeId=2

### Start reservation (vehicle pickup)
PATCH http://localhost:8080/api/reservations/1/start?pickupMileage=25000&fuelLevel=Full&vehicleCondition=Excellent condition, no damages&employeeId=2

### Complete reservation (vehicle return)
PATCH http://localhost:8080/api/reservations/1/complete?returnMileage=25350&fuelLevel=Half&vehicleCondition=Good condition, minor scratch on rear bumper&additionalFees=50.00&notes=Late return fee applied&employeeId=2

### Cancel reservation
PATCH http://localhost:8080/api/reservations/1/cancel?cancellationReason=Customer requested cancellation due to travel change

